=== sw-cor24-rpg-ii Minimal RPG-II Demo (Chain REVR00 + Third Output Shape) ===
Program:
H  control header
F  input file INFIL
I  field 01: A0110  (10-char input slice)
I  field 02: A0810  (3-char input tail slice)
C  REVR01 -> calc stage 0
C  REVR00 -> calc stage 1 reverses the current calc result
O  DETAIL01 output (10 chars)
O  DETAIL02 output (3 chars)
O  DETAIL03 output (6 chars)

Current boundary:
- Real today: calc slot 1 can still work over source selector 00 while stage 0
  drives the third output-shape selection.
- This variant composes REVR01 with REVR00, so the second calc stage cancels
  the first reversal and DETAIL03 emits the 6-byte field-01 prefix.

Current runtime-produced output:
RECORD
RECORD
RECORD

